If you want to contribute, please consider one or more of the following options in the given order:

- fork the repository, commit your changes, make a pull request
- open an issue: https://pss-gitlab.math.univ-paris-diderot.fr/data-processing-wg/seisglitch/issues
- contact the lead author of the code and paper: john.robert.scholz@gmail.com
- contact any other co-author